      • neighbors

        public java.lang.Iterable<MovecraftLocation> neighbors(MovecraftLocation location)
        finds the axial neighbors to a location. Neighbors are defined as locations that exist within one meter of a given location
        Parameters:
        location - the location to search for neighbors
        Returns:
        an iterable set of neighbors to the given location

      • exterior

        public HashHitBox exterior()
        Gets a HitBox that represents the "exterior" of this HitBox. The exterior is defined as the region of all location accessible from the six bounding planes of the hitbox before encountering a location contained in the original HitBox. Functions similarly to a flood fill but in three dimensions
        Returns:
        the exterior HitBox
